Package ie.gmit.dip

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Parser
    Interface for implementing in concrete classes which deals with parsing web and text sources for words included in the source.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ArrayListFileReader
    ArrayListFileReader implements Parser interface.
    CommandLineUI
    Provides the menu display options and user input functionality.
    FrequencyTable
    Creates a frequency table of words present in a source file or webpage.
    ImagePrint
    Provides the functionality of creating the word cloud image of the desired user input source.
    MapSorter
    The class MapSorter provides the sorting functionality of a Map based on the Integer value.
    Runner
    Provides the runner class of the WordCloud Application.
    WebPageReader
    The class WebPageReader implements Parser interface.
    WordCloud
    The class WordCloud is the main class in the WordCloud program which has dependencies to other secondary implementation classes for WordCloud program.
